Betfred to Announce Bid for Bookmaker Tote Tomorrow, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-16T21:03:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/betfred-to-announce-bid-for-bookmaker-tote-tomorrow-sky-says.html
Betfred Ltd. will tomorrow announce
details of its almost 200 million-pound ($324 million) bid for
the Tote, the  U.K.’s state-owned bookmaker, Sky News  reported 
on a blog on its website, without citing anyone.  Betfred’s statement will say it would make an annual
payment to the racing industry, which would be 11 million pounds
in the first year, Sky said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 